--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 1
Use case        : logout
Scenario name   : customer logout
Description     :

1. Login as customer.
2. Follow the links Profilo->Logout.

Expected results:

1. Redirect to the home page.
2. The customer in the header will disappear.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 2
Use case        : logout
Scenario name   : administrator logout
Description     :

1. Login as administrator.
2. Follow the links Profilo->Logout.

Expected results:

1. Redirect to the home page.
2. The administrator in the header will disappear.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 3
Use case        : logout
Scenario name   : user not logged try to logout using the url directly.
Description     :

1. Start from home page with no user logged.
2. Type the following urls into the address bar of the browser:

    http://<host>:<port>/<context>/jsp/users/Logout.jsp

Expected results:

1. Redirect to the home page.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

